OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FCanadian Prime Minister Mark Carney
OL,7,Fhas called for Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,8,FWindsor to be removed from the royal
OL,9,Fline of succession over his
OL,10,F"deplorable" links to Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,12,FThe former duke was arrested in
OL,13,FFebruary on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,14,Fpublic office following allegations he
OL,15,Fshared sensitive information with the
OL,16,Fpaedophile financier while serving as
OL,17,Fthe UK's trade envoy.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@LO]
