OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772935393
OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters in Tokyo, Mr
OL,7,FCarney said: "I certainly think his
OL,8,Factions are deplorable and have caused
OL,9,Fhim to be stripped of his royal
OL,10,Ftitles, certainly merit, if that's the
OL,11,Fword ` necessitate is a better word `
OL,12,Fhis removal from the line of
OL,13,Fsuccession."
OL,15,FThe prime ministers of Australia and
OL,16,FNew Zealand have previously said they
OL,17,Fwould support the UK Government in any
OL,18,Fplans to remove Andrew from the line
OL,19,Fof succession.
OL,26,@oD@NOUuD@LO]
