OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772935393
OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FSuch a move would require an Act of
OL,7,FParliament and the agreement of the
OL,8,FCommonwealth realms, including Canada.
OL,10,FMr Carney, a former governor of the
OL,11,FBank of England, added: "Even though
OL,12,Fhe is well down the line, the point of
OL,13,Fprinciple stands."
OL,15,FAndrew has denied any wrongdoing over
OL,16,Fhis links to the convicted sex
OL,17,Foffender, but has not directly
OL,18,Fresponded to the latest allegations.
OL,26,@sD@YOUuD@RO]
