OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FHe spent around 11 hours in custody in
OL,7,FFebruary as searches were conducted at
OL,8,Fhis home on the Sandringham Estate in
OL,9,FNorfolk and at his former home, Royal
OL,10,FLodge in Windsor, Berkshire, and
OL,11,Freleased pending investigation
OL,13,FAndrew served as the UK's special
OL,14,Frepresentative for international trade
OL,15,Fand investment from 2001 until 2011,
OL,16,Fwhen he stepped down amid controversy
OL,17,Fover his friendship with Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
