OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FThe UK Government will consider
OL,7,Fintroducing such legislation once
OL,8,Fpolice have finished their
OL,9,Finvestigation into the King's
OL,10,Fdisgraced brother, the Press
OL,11,FAssociation understands.
OL,13,FIn a letter to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer in February, Australian Prime
OL,15,FMinister Anthony Albanese said Andrew
OL,16,Fwas facing "grave allegations",
OL,17,Fadding: "Australians take them
OL,18,Fseriously".
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@^O]yD@IOUzD@JO]
