OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Christopher Luxon,
OL,7,FNew Zealand's prime minister, said:
OL,8,F"If the UK Government proposes to
OL,9,Fremove Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor from
OL,10,Fthe order of succession, New Zealand
OL,11,Fwould support it.
OL,13,F"The UK Government has said any
OL,14,Fproposals would come after the police
OL,15,Finvestigation concludes."
OL,17,FDefence Secretary John Healey last
OL,18,Fmonth ordered a review of military
OL,19,Ffiles for any evidence that Epstein
OL,20,Fused RAF bases to traffic girls into
OL,21,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUwD@YO]
