OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772935393
OL,3,CCanadian PM calls for Andrew to be
OL,4,Cremoved from line of succession
OL,6,FMr Healey tasked officials with
OL,7,Ftrawling through more than two decades
OL,8,Fof Ministry of Defence records and
OL,9,Fhanding over to police any flight logs
OL,10,Flinked to the late paedophile
OL,11,Ffinancier.
OL,13,FIt comes after former prime minister
OL,14,FGordon Brown wrote to six police
OL,15,Fforces demanding investigations into
OL,16,Fwhether Andrew used jets, funded by
OL,17,Fthe taxpayer, and RAF bases during his
OL,18,Ftime as trade envoy to meet Epstein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
